COMPANY LEAVE POLICY
Annual Leave:
Employees are entitled to 20 dys of annual leave per calendar year.
Sick Leave:
Employees are entitled to 10 days of paid sick leave per year.
Casual Leave:
Employees are entitled to 5 days of casual leave per year.
Maternity Leave:
Eligible employees are entitled to 180 days of maternity leave.
Paternity Leave:
Eligible employees are entitled to 15 days of paternity leave.
Leave Approval Process:
All leave requests must be submitted through the HR portal and approved by the reporting manager.
Leave Carry Forward:
A maximum of 5 unused annual leave days may be carried forward to the next calendar year.
Leave Encashment:
Unused annual leave may be encashed according to company policy during final settlement.
